\NeedsTeXFormat{LaTeX2e}
\documentclass{minimal}
\makeatletter
\def\RestoreCatcodes{}
\count@=0 %
\loop
  \edef\RestoreCatcodes{%
    \RestoreCatcodes
    \catcode\the\count@=\the\catcode\count@\relax
  }%
\ifnum\count@<255 %
  \advance\count@\@ne
\repeat

\def\RangeCatcodeInvalid#1#2{%
  \count@=#1\relax
  \loop
    \catcode\count@=15 %
  \ifnum\count@<#2\relax
    \advance\count@\@ne
  \repeat
}
\def\Test{%
  \RangeCatcodeInvalid{0}{47}%
